function.name: easy_qr_code_generator.create_qr_code
function.description: This tool generates QR codes that can be used to link to URLs, display text, or store other types of data. The resulting QR codes can be downloaded and printed for use in various applications, such as marketing materials, business cards, or event tickets.

function.name: qr_code_api_v33.qr_code_image
function.description: This endpoint accepts a GET request with a URL parameter that generates a QR code image in response. The resulting QR code can be processed or displayed as needed without any additional input requirements. It supports generating QR code images from strings, and an alternative endpoint (qr_code_api_v33.generate_qr_code_image) is available for URLs.
